## Verification Strategy

### Task 05 (Integration)

```yaml
Verification_Strategy:
  Test_Type: integration
  Test_Stack: Python / pytest + manual
  Acceptance_Criteria:
    - "SwarmEnv.reset() at Stage 5 sends 5 combat rules (4 base + 1 AoE cone)"
    - "SwarmEnv.reset() at Stage 6 sends 5 combat rules (4 base + 1 AoE circle)"  
    - "SwarmEnv.reset() at Stage 7 sends 5 combat rules + unit_types payload"
    - "Stage 8 correctly delegates to sub-stage combat rules"
    - "No regression: Stages 0-4 reset payloads unchanged"
  Manual_Steps:
    - "Run training at Stage 5, observe AoE cone damage in debug visualizer"
    - "Verify brain dies on frontal charge (combat math validation)"
```

